edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"拖得耐其實維持係好難<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港自由之書&mdash;賣卡投資國難五金發國難財Ver 2.0</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1486618/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1486618/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1df3ce6a9f2a761b7a524e11f0ac3e4f4fcb3986","tid":1486544,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:48:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}